-- Fed declines comment on AIG conservatorship news report
-- 
-- Tue Sep 16, 2008 5:25pm EDT
-- http://www.reuters.com/article/2008/09/16/us-aig-fed-conservatorship-idUSWBT00972820080916

 

 WASHINGTON  (Reuters) - The U.S. Federal Reserve declined to comment on Tuesday on a report by Bloomberg that the government was considering placing in conservatorship struggling insurer American International Group Inc. 

 The Fed had no comment on the report, spokeswoman Michelle Smith said. (Reporting by  Mark Felsenthal )